{
  "name": "WF-06-AGENT-ROUTER-V1",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## WF-06 — Agent Router V1\n**Exército Comercial de IA — Roteador Proativo**\n\nRoda a cada 5 minutos via cron.\nBusca TODOS os agentes ativos, checa horário de trabalho,\nfaz a fila de leads de cada agente e dispara WF-07.\n\n**Fluxo:**\nSchedule → Get Agents → Loop → Check Hours →\nGet Queue → Get Conversation → Loop → Trigger WF-07\n\n**URL do WF-07:** configure AGENT_EXECUTOR_WEBHOOK_URL nas env vars do n8n.\n(ex: https://seu-n8n.com/webhook/agent-executor)",
        "height": 240,
        "width": 460,
        "color": 6
      },
      "id": "wf06-note-001",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        0,
        -160
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "cronExpression",
              "expression": "*/5 * * * *"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
